snippet: Phelps’s winning time, 50.45 seconds, was faster than Chad Le Clos’s time about eight hours earlier in Kazan, Russia, where Le Clos won the world championship in 50.56.
abstract: Michael Phelps wins 100-meter butterfly at national championships in San Antonio in 50.45 seconds, beating Chad Le Clos's time about eight hours earlier in Kazan, Russia, where Le Clos won world championship. in 50.56.
